sequenceDiagram
  participant User as Användare
  participant Client as Publik Klient (t.ex. Mobilapp)
  participant AuthorizationServer as Auktoriseringsserver
  participant ResourceServer as Resursserver

  User ->> Client: Initierar Autentisering
  Client ->> AuthorizationServer: POST /registration
  AuthorizationServer -->> Client: { "client_id": "klient-id-här" }

  Client ->> User: Presenterar Klient ID för Godkännande
  User -->> Client: Godkänner Klient

  Client ->> AuthorizationServer: GET /authorize?response_type=code&client_id=klient-id-här&redirect_uri=callback-url&code_challenge=verifier-här&code_challenge_method=S256
  AuthorizationServer ->> User: Ber om Inloggning och Auktorisering
  User -->> AuthorizationServer: Loggar in och Godkänner

  AuthorizationServer -->> Client: 302 Found (Redirect till callback-url?code=auktoriseringskod-här)

  Client ->> AuthorizationServer: POST /token
  AuthorizationServer -->> Client: { "access_token": "åtkomsttoken-här", "token_type": "bearer", "expires_in": 3600 }

  Client ->> ResourceServer: GET /skyddad-resurs
  ResourceServer ->> AuthorizationServer: Validerar Åtkomsttoken och DPOP
  AuthorizationServer ->> ResourceServer: 200 OK (Åtkomsttoken och DPOP Validering)

  ResourceServer -->> Client: 200 OK (Skyddad Resurs)
